§ Why ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ What are addition and multiplication for integers? ⦉

  ‖ What are the identity elements? ⦉
⦉

§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ We call the operation of forming integer sums ❬integer
    addition❭. ⦉

  ‖ We call the operation of forming integer products ❬integer
    multiplication❭. ⦉
⦉

